      "path": "/books/al-amali-saduq:51:8",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/29/1/52/8",
      "text": [
        ": قال رسول الله (صلى الله عليه وآله): قال الله جل جلاله: يا بن آدم، اذكرني بعد الغداة ساعة وبعد العصر ساعة أكفك ما أهمك (3)."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bilal-muhammad": [
          "By this isnad, he said: The Messenger of Allah (s) said: Allah said: O son of Adam! Remember Me for a moment after morning and for a moment after `Asr, and I will suffice you from what worries you."
        ]
      }
    },
